Mura Masa will play at Rocking the Daisies 2018. The 22-year-old electronic music producer was born in Castel, Guernsey and is the second act that the organisers of the big local music festival have announced. Rocking the Daisies broke the news on their Twitter account on Monday afternoon closely after announcing that rapper Goldlink would also be playing at the festival. Rocking the Daisies 2018 will take place from Friday, 5 until Sunday, 7 October. Source: Channel24 Music